description:
Danny welcomes Hannah Brown to recap this week's Real Housewives of Orange County. They talk about Vicki's return, Gina's everything, Braunwyn's sex condo, and more! Then Danny recaps the Southern Charm finale, which centered around a ball and an ambush.


Southern Charm Recap: 35:03ish
